		<main>
			<div>
				<h2>Product Description</h2>
				<div class="main-container">
					<div class="description-text">
						<h1>@Model.Title</h1>

						<p>These figures are pre-owned and have been carefully examined and photographed before being listed.</p>
						<h3>Condition:</h3>
						<p>@Model.Condition</p>
						<p><em>Please choose from the drop-down menu above to select the minifigure of your choice.</em></p>
						<p>We sell a large variety of Lego Minifigures, including new and used figures from sets, as well as collectable minifigures. If you buy 2 or more figures, we will deduct <em>10% off at checkout.</em></p>
					</div>

					<a target="_blank" href="https://www.ebay.co.uk/sme/coolcat-collectables/Buy-2-Get-10-off/so.html?_soffType=OrderSubTotalOffer&_soffid=6080920504">
