		--><label for="tab4">Contact</label><!--
		--><section id="about">
			<p>Hello and thank you for visiting our shop!</p>
			<p>We are a couple of friendly collectible toy enthusiasts based in Lancaster, 
			specialising in selling Lego and Minifigures.</p>
			<p>Being collectors ourselves, we care very much about the quality of our products and aim to deliver to the highest standard.</p>
			<p>We are only small at the moment, but are working on expanding our store in the coming months, so please do add us to
			your favourites.</p>
			<p>Any feedback or comments are welcomed and much appreciated.</p>
		</section>
		<section id="payment">
			<p>We accept payment via Debit, Credit Card &amp; PayPal via the secure PayPal checkout onsite.</p>
			<picture class="paypal">
				<source media="(min-width: 370px)" srcset="https://www.paypalobjects.com/webstatic/mktg/Logo/AM_mc_vs_ms_ae_UK.png">
				<img src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/webstatic/mktg/logo/bdg_payments_by_pp_2line.png" alt="Thanks for visiting cool cat collects!">
			</picture>
		</section>
		<section id="shipping">
			<p>We will ship your order within 24 hours of received payment, Monday-Friday. The cut off time on Friday for same day dispatch is 2pm.</p>
			<p>Shipping is free for all UK orders, regardless of how much you buy.</p>
			<p>International orders start at £2.80 and will be sent via Royal Mail International standard post.</p>
			<p>International tracking is available on request for an additional cost of £4. Please select postage option at checkout.</p>
			<p>Please note: International orders may be subject to import duties and taxes which are levied once a shipment reaches your country. 
				<br/>Additional charges for custom clearance must be borne by the buyer. Please check your local customs rates for further information.</p>
		</section>
		<section id="returns">
			<p>If you are not 100% satisfied with your purchase, you can return your item and get a full refund within 30 days from the date of purchase.</p>
			<p>All we ask is that you return the item to us in the same condition that you received it.</p>
		</section>
		<section id="contact">
			<p>If you have any questions, feedback or problems with your order, please contact us directly via the eBay messaging service.</p>
			<p>While we make every best effort to fulfill all our orders to the highest standard, sometimes mistakes do happen. 
				<br/>We will resolve any problems as quickly as possible.</p>
			<p>We aim to respond within 24 hours, however please allow a little longer over the weekend and public holidays.</p>
		</section>
	</section>
	<picture id="footer-banner">
		<source media="(min-width: 981px)" srcset="https://i.ibb.co/5hq6NdW/Listing-Footer-1393x150-v1-1.jpg">
